# User-state folder. The bundled defaults live in `default_settings/`
# (tracked) and are merged into `settings/` on first run by
# defaults_sync.py. Never track the user's `settings/` -- it holds
# their own presets, char assignments, optimizer config, etc.
# Also where config.json lives as of round 11 (was at the repo root).
settings/
